            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Hd1e108">Rubrica 7</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De contentionibus</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>
      ¶ De contentionibus. Rubrica. 7.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>SAlomon in prouerb. c. 3
      <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e125">Ne contendas
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>l aduersus hominem frustra. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e131"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e133"> 24. c. Ne
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>contendas cum pessimis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e140"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e142"> 20. c. Ho
        <lb ed="#V" n="76" break="no"/>norem homin qui se separat a contentionibus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e148">
               <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e152">/ 29. c. Uir sapiens si cum stulto contenderit si
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>ue irascatur siue rideat: non inueniet requiem. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e158">
               <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e162">¶ Iesus filius sirach in eccl. c. 8. Non litiges
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>cum homine linguato: et ne strtas ignem illus lingi </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e168">
               <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e172">/ 11. c. De ea re que te non molestat ne cer
        <lb ed="#V" n="82" break="no"/>taueris. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e178">
               <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e182">¶ Oratius in epistolis li. i. e. 19. Alter rixatur de
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>lana sepe caprina. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e188">
               <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e192">¶ Paulus apostolus in epistola. 2. ad timotheum. c. 2.
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>Noli verbis contendere: ad nihilum enim vti
        <lb ed="#V" n="87" break="no"/>le est: nisi ad subuersionem audientium. Ineptas
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>et sine disciplina questiones de uita: sciens
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>quia generant lites. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e205">
               <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e209">¶ Seneca de ira li. 2. Cum pari contendere <!--116.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="45-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>ancepes est: cum superiore furiosum: cum in
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>feriore sordidum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e223">
               <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e227">¶ Lex diges. ti. de seruitu. vr praedi. l. iure coni.
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>Propter immensas cogitationes plerumque res
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>ad diuisionem peruenit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e235">
               <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e239">¶ Auctor li. de formula honeste vite. ca. 4.
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>Contendenti facile cede: nec iniurgia discepta
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>tionesque descendas. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e247">
               <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e251">¶ Ambrosius de officiis li. i. c. 2. Absit perti
        <lb ed="#V" n="10" break="no"/>nax in familiari sermone contentio: questio
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>nes enim magis excitare inanes quam vtilita
        <lb ed="#V" n="12" break="no"/>tis aliquid afferre solet. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e261">
               <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e265">¶ Macrobius saturnaliorum li. 2. c. 18 exau.
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>liberii: Nimium altercando veritas amittitur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e271">
               <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e275">¶ Cato. c. 2. Contra verbosos noli contende
        <lb ed="#V" n="16" break="no"/>re verbis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e282"> ¶
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e284">¶ Cato. ca. 3.
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>Aduersum notu noli contendere verbis.
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>Lis minimis verbis: interdum maxima crescit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e292">
               <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e296">¶ Isidorus solilo. li. 2. c. 26 Caue contentiones
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>Contentio rixas gignit.
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>Contentio faces odiorum accendit.
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>Contentio pacem cordis extinguit.
        <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>Contentio concordiam rumpit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-d1e308">
               <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d33955-Qd1e312">/ Libro. 2. c. 43 Cede cito veritati.
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>In omni disputatione tene rationem. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
